51
00:03:44,080 --> 00:03:49,840
It all starts with my own pain at work that I want to solve and then I look for solutions for that pain.

52
00:03:49,840 --> 00:03:55,360
And if I don't find the solutions on the market, then I go and talk about this pain on the internet.

53
00:03:55,360 --> 00:04:02,000
And if I see other people resonate with my pain and they say,"Yeah, I have the same pain and I I wish there was a solution."

54
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:04,879
Then that's kind of grand signal for me to go to the next step.

55
00:04:04,879 --> 00:04:10,879
I launch uh a weight list and I see whether I am able to generate 100 signups.

56
00:04:10,879 --> 00:04:17,199
I email them all and I offer them 90% discount on a pre-sale before I build anything.

57
00:04:17,199 --> 00:04:20,959
And then if I get five sales, I build the first MVP.

58
00:04:20,959 --> 00:04:22,320
I don't even build a product.

59
00:04:22,320 --> 00:04:24,880
I actually deliver the solution manually.

60
00:04:24,880 --> 00:04:28,080
At this stage, I don't care about the margins yet.

61
00:04:28,080 --> 00:04:33,280
I just care about the solution being delivered to the customers and whether they actually satisfied with that.

62
00:04:33,280 --> 00:04:35,280
