63
00:04:35,280 --> 00:04:39,759
Usually I have to iterate and I deliver solution to the customers and they don't like it.

64
00:04:39,759 --> 00:04:42,320
So I iterate iterate until they like it.

65
00:04:42,320 --> 00:04:45,919
