26 businesses, 3 million AR is amazing.

243
00:17:00,320 --> 00:17:03,040
It's only going to keep growing and I'm stoked to watch your journey.

244
00:17:03,040 --> 00:17:04,880
Thanks for coming on and sharing all that.

245
00:17:04,880 --> 00:17:06,079
Thanks for having me.

246
